cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CR 

This paper is about semantic segmentation, which is a computer vision task, so cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a new network architecture and explores different methods to improve recall rate, which involves machine learning and optimization techniques, so cs.LG and cs.AI are also likely sub-categories. The application of semantic segmentation in autonomous vehicles and navigation assistance systems suggests that cs.RO (robotics) could also be a relevant sub-category. Finally, the evaluation of the proposed methods involves comparing performance on state-of-the-art datasets, which could fall under cs.CR (computing research).
